Nestled in the middle of the Heartland you'll find Sioux Falls, SD. Sioux Falls has a booming developer community, we're also known as the &ldquo;Silicon Prairie.&rdquo;
The Sioux Falls Developer's Group is open to developers in the area. Each month we bring in speakers to present on a wide variety of software development topics. Once a year, we put on a developer centric conference, South Dakota Code Camp.
